text.tspan: After the Learning Phase (III): Finding and Filtering Patches
- finding: adjacent hot samples are joined together into patches
- filtering: patches satisfying criteria are called blips
- minimum and maximum numbers of samples in the patch
- minimum and maximum apparent patch area
- minimum and maximum angular span of patch
- minimum and maximum radial span of patch
- reclassify blip samples: sample_class[i, j] = blip
